Organization Name: PUBLIC TRANSIT SERVICES (PTS) | PALO PINTO AND PARKER COUNTY TRANSIT OFFICE | TRANSPORTATION SERVICES
Description: Provides public and demand response curb to curb transportation service.

Organization Name: TRINITY METRO | MAIN OFFICE | NORTH TEXAS XPRESS
Description: Provides bus service connecting Fort Worth and Denton with stops in Alliance through partnership between Trinity Metro and the Denton County Transportation Authority (DCTA).

Provides public transportation services to the citizens of Tarrant County to include fixed route bus service as well as Trinity Railway Express which is commuter rail service jointly owned and operated with Dallas Area Rapid Transit (DART) connecting downtown Fort Worth to downtown Dallas.
